{"tid":1461768,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[另類] [打鬼] 鵝頸橋7月14之鬼打鬼","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:04:42.000Z","uid":140041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12d89b720c539b761d3bdc1ca19db2e719e0b0d3","tid":1461768,"uid":140041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:12:51.000Z","msg":"Hi, 又到 [另類] [和理非] 時間<br />\n之前個Post得到大家熱烈討論<br />\n[另類] [風水] 中共係咪爆左條龍脈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1368339/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1368339/page/1</a><br />\n小人心感安慰<br />\n拿, 眼見大家都暫不勇武而作為和理非既一員<br />\n集合之前個Post 回覆大家都想試下另類抗共方法<br />\n有個建議: <span style=\"color: gold;\">本人熱愛古中國文化, 主張非暴力<br />\n聽日8月14日(適逢農歷7月14日正日) <br />\n而人間鬼魅當道, 神鬼不分<br />\n正正需要正能量打死香港真小人 / 打鬼</span><br />\n根據香港旅遊發展局介紹<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.discoverhongkong.com/tc/see-do/culture-heritage/living-culture/petty-person-beating.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.discoverhongkong.com%2Ftc%2Fsee-do%2Fculture-heritage%2Fliving-culture%2Fpetty-person-beating.jsp&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb%2BF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=7d6425de\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.discoverhongkong.com/tc/see-do/culture-heritage/living-culture/petty-person-beating.jsp</a><br />\n聽日大家可以各自去銅鑼灣鵝頸橋底<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">打&middot;小&middot;人</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有一d有用資料比大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgPU59J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgPU59J.jpg&h=80b269f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打小人口訣<br />\n<br />\n打小人，係廣東民間流行嘅一種巫術儀祀，希望咁樣可以趕走同報復所謂［小人］。最多人打小人會喺［驚蟄］呢個日子，而香港最多人打小人同表演打小人嘅地方就喺鵝頸橋［堅拿道天橋底］。<br />\n<br />\n打小人儀式，聽講話係源自道教嘅祭白虎儀式，成個儀式有八個部分：<br />\n。奉神<br />\n。稟告<br />\n。打小人<br />\n。祭白虎<br />\n。化解<br />\n。祈福<br />\n。進寶<br />\n。打杯［筊］<br />\n<br />\n打小人嘅架生：<br />\n。肥豬肉<br />\n。生雞蛋<br />\n。生果<br />\n。綠豆<br />\n。二手鞋  ［咩鞋都得］<br />\n。小人公仔紙［有男有女］<br />\n。紙扎白老虎<br />\n。衣寶香燭<br />\nby 我愛廣東話。廣東話資料館<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CantoneseMuseum/photos/a.519042431439307/1096555077021370/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCantoneseMuseum%2Fphotos%2Fa.519042431439307%2F1096555077021370%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb%2BF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=a0bd0924\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CantoneseMuseum/photos/a.519042431439307/1096555077021370/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2144609/%E3%80%90%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E3%80%91%E7%9B%82%E8%98%AD%E5%8B%9D%E6%9C%83%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%85%E9%A9%9A%E6%85%8C%E3%80%80%E6%8E%8C%E6%95%85%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%96%E7%9B%A1%E7%9B%82%E8%98%AD%E7%BF%92%E4%BF%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2144609%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E6%259B%2586%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259C%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%259B%2582%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%258B%259D%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%2585%25E9%25A9%259A%25E6%2585%258C%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%2595%2585%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25AB%2596%25E7%259B%25A1%25E7%259B%2582%25E8%2598%25AD%25E7%25BF%2592%25E4%25BF%2597&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb%2BF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=404bd888\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2144609/%E3%80%90%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E4%B8%83%E6%9C%88%E3%80%91%E7%9B%82%E8%98%AD%E5%8B%9D%E6%9C%83%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%85%E9%A9%9A%E6%85%8C%E3%80%80%E6%8E%8C%E6%95%85%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%96%E7%9B%A1%E7%9B%82%E8%98%AD%E7%BF%92%E4%BF%97</a><br />\n不過，他相信這個鬼節盛會如「打小人」般不只延續下去，還會在年輕人間流行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199018670f865e266ea04b5f4f78714f81959232","tid":1461768,"uid":140041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:14:35.000Z","msg":"<bloc